text: Tamaqua is a borough in Schuylkill County, Pennsylvania, United States. It also has public schools.https://www.tamaqua.k12.pa.us/ In 2020, 6,916 people were in Tamaqua. It was founded in 1832.https://semspub.epa.gov/work/03/17121.pdf == List of schools == School name Founded First day of school date Last day of school date Tamaqua Elementary School TBA August 28 June 5 == References == Category:Boroughs in Pennsylvania
